Message:<dfn>In the message, you may use $userid, $username, $email, $activateid, and $activatelink.<br /><br />$activateid will be the activation number the user must use to activate his/her account. $activatelink will be the URL that a user needs to visit to be  activated. <i>Note: These will only be defined to users in the "Users Awaiting Email Confirmation" group.</i><br /><br /><b>Note:</b> you cannot send passwords using this form as they are encrypted in the database. Please link to the 'lost password' form instead.</dfn>